nodes.text: "Rescued Aliens: The Trompa" was a web article featuring the trompa that was written by Owen K.C. Stephens and Steve Miller and released by Wizards of the Coast as a supplement to the Star Wars Roleplaying Game sourcebook Alien Anthology. The article content was originally supposed to be included in the book, but was cut for space and released on the Wizards of the Coast website instead.
